modName: Female Preset for BetrayalSeeker's Snow Elf Overhaul
summary: This is my PC that I made using the Snow Elf Overhaul by BetrayalSeeker, that I am sharing with you all today.
descriptionHtml:
Requires Dawnguard and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36777/?]Snow elf Overhaul[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/6768323/?]BetrayalSeeker[/url].

A simple preset for RaceMenu. Download it manually and put it into Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets.

To get the eyes how they look in my screenshots:
1) Manually download [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3589/?]Natural Eyes[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/942284/?]nevenbridge81[/url], you can get either the Hi res or normal version 1.4
2) Extract the file to your prefered location and look for the wood and high elf eyes
3) Copy the blue ones to BetrayalSeeker's snow elf texture folder (in Skyrim/Data/texture/snow elf), rename, and overwrite his eyes

Feel free to upload your own screenshots with her :-)

*Note: The brightness of her face in my screenshots is caused by RaceMenu, her skin is darker in-game

Dank je wel.
author: RavenSterling
